Some future ToDos
=================

* PCAPng support
* ARP cache poisoning for Man-In-The-Middle sniffing
* Adding tons of protocols to decode
* Statistical anomaly detection for netsniff-ng-server
* netsniff-ng-server that provides network statistics for user clients
  (e.g. Nagios)
* Kernelcode improvements in af_packet.c

There are also some information about future plans within our 
frequently asked questions page: http://netsniff-ng.org/faq.html
